                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- pricing item -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-md-50">
                        <div class="rounded border">
                            <div class="p-4 border-bottom">
                                <h2 class="font-weight-bold mb-3">£25<span class="h5">/month</span>
                                </h2>                                <i class="square-icon translateY-10 float-right ti-gift"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-5 px-4">

                                <p>Could pay for two one-to-one project work sessions, helping a homeless person address issues in their life and make steps forward.</p>

                                <a href="{{ baseUrl }}donate-regularly?amount=25.00" class="btn btn-primary translateY-25">Donate</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- pricing item -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-md-50">
                        <div class="rounded border">
                            <div class="p-4 border-bottom">
                                <h2 class="font-weight-bold mb-3">£50<span class="h5">/month</span></h2>
                                <i class="square-icon translateY-10 float-right ti-gift"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pt-5 px-4">
                                <p>Could provide travel costs for an individual (bus pass), so they can attend medical appointments and access support services.</p>
                                <a href="{{ baseUrl }}donate-regularly?amount=50.00" class="btn btn-primary translateY-25">Donate</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                  
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- /pricing -->

        <section class="cta bg-gray py-50 text-center text-lg-left" style="background-image: url('images/background/cta.jpg');">
            <div class="container">

                <div class="row justify-content-between">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                        <h2 class="mb-2">Make a one off donation</h2>
                        <p class="mb-5">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod
